You’ll need: 65ml butter, cut into blocks; 15ml ground cinnamon; 2.5ml ground nutmeg; 2 x 410g can Rhodes Quality Apricot Halves, drained For the batter – 250ml self-rising flour; 190ml butter, melted; 190ml sugar; 3 eggs; 10ml vanilla essence To serve – whipped cream or ice cream, How to: Serve warm with whipped cream, ice cream or custard. * Recipe & image by Rhodes Quality.